N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 328.5 - Annual report

State Regulations

On or before December 1st of each year, the chancellor
shall make an annual report to the board of trustees for the previous year, concerning the affairs of the university and recommendations with respect
thereto. Notes
